# Component versions for the kubernetes-kubeadm-1node backend image
# (also used by the 2-node backend). This is the SINGLE place to set the
# Kubernetes and Cilium versions — edit here, then rebuild:
#
#   docker build -t ghcr.io/rockops/rockdemo/kubernetes-kubeadm-1node:24.04 \
#     docker/kubernetes-kubeadm-1node
#
# Everything else follows automatically at build time: the apt package pins, the
# apt repo minor, all control-plane image tags (via kubeadm), the Cilium image
# tags in the manifest, and the pre-pulled image cache (derived from the above).
# See VERSIONS.md for the full story.

# Kubernetes patch version — kubelet / kubeadm / kubectl and every control-plane
# image (apiserver, etcd, coredns, kube-proxy, pause). Use a full x.y.z; the apt
# repo minor (pkgs.k8s.io is per-minor) is derived from it.
KUBERNETES_VERSION=1.33.1

# Cilium version — the cilium agent + operator images. NOTE: the coupled
# cilium-envoy image has its own release tag (not equal to this version) and is
# pinned in manifests/cilium-cni.yaml. It stays constant across Cilium PATCH
# releases, so a patch bump only needs this line; when bumping the Cilium MINOR,
# also update the cilium-envoy tag in the manifest.
CILIUM_VERSION=1.16.1
